Students exit the event with these tote bags and a stack of business cards.

A welcome announcement outlines the fair schedule over the PA system, while career counselors guide unsure students toward relevant industries and remind attendees to maintain eye contact. An aroma of coffee and catered snacks spreads from the lounge. A robotics startup draws attention by flying a small drone above its booth, and its founder invites students to a lunchtime pitch session. The dean visits to thank recruiters for their support. As the day progresses, announcement chimes signal the final hour of the fair, interview sign-up sheets fill with names, and workshops on networking etiquette commence in an adjoining classroom. Human resources teams take notes on tablets as students introduce themselves, and they utilize tablets at kiosks to upload their resumes to the fair database. Finance firms offer QR codes for immediate internship applications, and recruiters remind students to follow up with personalized emails. Additionally, a post-event survey link flashes on the monitors near the exit.
